Change Decimal No. to its Binary form.

PROBLEM: I/P- N=2
         O/P- 000000000000000000000000000010        (30 bit)
         
SOLUTION:

    string getBinaryRep(int N)
    {
        for(int i=29; i>=0; i--){
            int a= N>>i;
            if(a & 1) cout<<"1";
            else cout<<"0";
        }
    }
